Package: HEMAscRaper
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Scraping and Analyzing HEMA Ratings Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Giuliano Gianneti
Maintainer: Giuliano Gianneti <giuliano@seznam.cz>
Description: HEMAscRaper provides tools to scrape data from the Historical European Martial Arts (HEMA) Ratings website. 
    It includes functions to download and parse information on fighters, clubs, events, and tournament results. 
    The package is designed to facilitate analysis and exploration of HEMA data, making it easy for users to access structured 
    information for research, visualization, or integration with other datasets.
    The package uses `rvest` for web scraping and `dplyr` for data manipulation, ensuring compatibility with common R workflows.
